n, m = map(int, input().split())
    a = list(map(int, input().split()))
    a.insert(0, 0)
    a.append(0)
    dp = [[0 for i in range(m+1)] for j in range(n+1)]
    for i in range(1, n+1):
        for j in range(1, m+1):
            dp[i][j] = dp[i-1][j]
            if a[i] == j:
                dp[i][j] = min(dp[i][j], dp[i-1][j-1])
            dp[i][j] = min(dp[i][j], dp[i-1][j]+1)
    print(dp[n][m])

n = int(input())
    a = list(map(int, input().split()))
    a.sort()
    dp = [0] * (n + 1)
    dp[0] = 1
    for i in range(1, n + 1):
        for j in range(i):
            if a[i] % a[j] == 0:
                dp[i] += dp[j]
    print(dp[n] % 1000000007)
